#. <section class="sutta" id="sn8.6"><article><div class="hgroup"><p class="division">
msgctxt "sn8.6:0.1"
msgid "Saṃyutta Nikāya 8"
msgstr "Linked Discourses 8"

#. </p><p>
msgctxt "sn8.6:0.2"
msgid "1. Vaṅgīsavagga"
msgstr "1. With Vaṅgīsa"

#. </p><h1>
#. VAR: 6. Sāriputtasutta → sārīputtasuttaṃ (s3)
msgctxt "sn8.6:0.3"
msgid "6. Sāriputtasutta"
msgstr "6. With Sāriputta"

#. </h1></div><p>
#. <a class="pts1ed" id="pts1ed1.190"></a>
#. <a class="pts2ed" id="pts2ed1.409"></a>
#. <a class="sc" id="sc1"></a>
msgctxt "sn8.6:1.1"
msgid ""
"Ekaṃ samayaṃ āyasmā sāriputto sāvatthiyaṃ viharati jetavane anāthapiṇḍikassa "
"ārāme."
msgstr ""
"At one time Venerable Sāriputta was staying near Sāvatthī in Jeta’s Grove, "
"Anāthapiṇḍika’s monastery."

#. VAR: anelagalāya → aneḷagalāya (bj, pts2, mr) | anelagaḷāya (s1-3, km, pts1)
msgctxt "sn8.6:1.2"
msgid ""
"Tena kho pana samayena āyasmā sāriputto bhikkhū dhammiyā kathāya sandasseti "
"samādapeti samuttejeti sampahaṃseti poriyā vācāya vissaṭṭhāya anelagalāya "
"atthassa viññāpaniyā."
msgstr ""
"Now at that time Venerable Sāriputta was educating, encouraging, firing up, "
"and inspiring the mendicants in the assembly hall with a Dhamma talk. His "
"words were polished, clear, articulate, and expressed the meaning."

msgctxt "sn8.6:1.3"
msgid ""
"Te ca bhikkhū aṭṭhiṃ katvā manasi katvā sabbacetasā samannāharitvā ohitasotā "
"dhammaṃ suṇanti."
msgstr ""
"And those mendicants were paying attention, focusing, concentrating "
"wholeheartedly, and listening well."

msgctxt "sn8.6:1.4"
msgid "Atha kho āyasmato vaṅgīsassa etadahosi:"
msgstr "Then Venerable Vaṅgīsa thought:"

msgctxt "sn8.6:1.5"
msgid ""
"“ayaṃ kho āyasmā sāriputto bhikkhū dhammiyā kathāya sandasseti samādapeti "
"samuttejeti sampahaṃseti poriyā vācāya vissaṭṭhāya anelagalāya atthassa "
"viññāpaniyā."
msgstr "“This Venerable Sāriputta is educating the mendicants. …"

msgctxt "sn8.6:1.6"
msgid ""
"Te ca bhikkhū aṭṭhiṃ katvā manasi katvā sabbacetasā samannāharitvā ohitasotā "
"dhammaṃ suṇanti."
msgstr ""
"And those mendicants are paying attention, focusing, concentrating "
"wholeheartedly, and listening well."

msgctxt "sn8.6:1.7"
msgid ""
"Yannūnāhaṃ āyasmantaṃ sāriputtaṃ sammukhā sāruppāhi gāthāhi "
"abhitthaveyyan”ti."
msgstr "Why don’t I extoll him in his presence with appropriate verses?”"

#. </p><p>
#. <a class="sc" id="sc2"></a>
msgctxt "sn8.6:2.1"
msgid ""
"Atha kho āyasmā vaṅgīso uṭṭhāyāsanā ekaṃsaṃ uttarāsaṅgaṃ karitvā yenāyasmā "
"sāriputto tenañjaliṃ paṇāmetvā āyasmantaṃ sāriputtaṃ etadavoca:"
msgstr ""
"Then Venerable Vaṅgīsa got up from his seat, arranged his robe over one "
"shoulder, raised his joined palms toward Sāriputta, and said:"

msgctxt "sn8.6:2.2"
msgid "“paṭibhāti maṃ, āvuso sāriputta, paṭibhāti maṃ, āvuso sāriputtā”ti."
msgstr ""
"“I feel inspired to speak, Reverend Sāriputta! I feel inspired to speak, "
"Reverend Sāriputta!”"

msgctxt "sn8.6:2.3"
msgid "“Paṭibhātu taṃ, āvuso vaṅgīsā”ti."
msgstr "“Then speak as you feel inspired,” said Sāriputta."

msgctxt "sn8.6:2.4"
msgid ""
"Atha kho āyasmā vaṅgīso āyasmantaṃ sāriputtaṃ sammukhā sāruppāhi gāthāhi "
"abhitthavi:"
msgstr ""
"Then Vaṅgīsa extolled Sāriputta in his presence with appropriate verses:"

#. </p><blockquote class="gatha"><p>
#. <a class="sc" id="sc3"></a>
msgctxt "sn8.6:3.1"
msgid "“Gambhīrapañño medhāvī,"
msgstr "“Deep in wisdom, intelligent,"

#. <br>
msgctxt "sn8.6:3.2"
msgid "maggāmaggassa kovido;"
msgstr "expert in the variety of paths;"

#. <br>
msgctxt "sn8.6:3.3"
msgid "Sāriputto mahāpañño,"
msgstr "Sāriputta, so greatly wise,"

#. <br>
msgctxt "sn8.6:3.4"
msgid "dhammaṃ deseti bhikkhunaṃ."
msgstr "teaches Dhamma to the mendicants."

#. </p><p>
#. <a class="pts2ed" id="pts2ed1.410"></a>
#. <a class="sc" id="sc4"></a>
msgctxt "sn8.6:4.1"
msgid "Saṃkhittenapi deseti,"
msgstr "He teaches in brief,"

#. <br>
msgctxt "sn8.6:4.2"
msgid "vitthārenapi bhāsati;"
msgstr "or he speaks at length."

#. <br>
msgctxt "sn8.6:4.3"
msgid "Sāḷikāyiva nigghoso,"
msgstr "His call, like a myna bird,"

#. <br>
msgctxt "sn8.6:4.4"
msgid "paṭibhānaṃ udīrayi."
msgstr "overflows with inspiration."

#. </p><p>
#. <a class="sc" id="sc5"></a>
msgctxt "sn8.6:5.1"
msgid "Tassa taṃ desayantassa,"
msgstr "While he teaches"

#. <br>
msgctxt "sn8.6:5.2"
msgid "suṇanti madhuraṃ giraṃ;"
msgstr "the mendicants listen to his sweet voice,"

#. <br>
msgctxt "sn8.6:5.3"
msgid "Sarena rajanīyena,"
msgstr "sounding attractive,"

#. <br>
msgctxt "sn8.6:5.4"
msgid "savanīyena vaggunā;"
msgstr "clear and graceful."

#. <br>
msgctxt "sn8.6:5.5"
msgid "Udaggacittā muditā,"
msgstr "They listen joyfully,"

#. <br>
msgctxt "sn8.6:5.6"
msgid "sotaṃ odhenti bhikkhavo”ti."
msgstr "their hearts uplifted.”"
